text: Hi Krish, I'm a senior sales professional with 8 + years of experience in sales and business development. After 1st pandemic, I lost my job and since then, I had been in process to learn Data Science (Actually w.r.t. As I'm also into a situation to get a job. Due to different reasons, I did lose some interviews from my sales profile and I continue to be jobless, for almost an year. Only positive thing is, I didn't lose hope and learning process is still on. However, I still struggle to create a proper Data Science or Analyst Resume to apply for jobs and I also lack of the relevant experience in data analysis.
